    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in this fantastic vehicle that's in truly good condition! It has been well-cared for and offers a dependable, smooth performance that you'll love every time you get behind the wheel. The interior is clean and comfortable, making it the perfect choice for anyone seeking a reliable and attractive ride. This car is ready for its next adventure\u2014come see for yourself how well it handles!",
