    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, but the paint still retains a nice shine. Inside, the cabin is clean with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as they should, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
