      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order, though you should expect some minor cosmetic wear such as small scratches on the exterior and visible aging on the interior upholstery. It has been well-maintained for its age, but it is not a showroom piece and would benefit from a thorough detailing. This is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes functionality and value over aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
