      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved specimen, offered in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive maintenance, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition offers an unrivaled opportunity to own a vehicle of unparalleled caliber.",
