      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine\u2014the premium leather still carries that factory-fresh scent and shows no signs of wear. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and always stored in a climate-controlled garage. This isn't just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
